 F(x+p)=F(x)\quad  \mathrm{iff} \quad\int_{0}^{x+p}f(t) dt=\int_{0}^{x}f(t)dt + \int_{x}^{x+p}f(t)dt= \int_{0}^{x}f(t)dt 
 \mathrm{iff} \quad\int_{x}^{x+p}f(t) dt = 0 \quad  \mathrm{iff} \quad\int_{0}^{p}f(t) dt = 0 .
